{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act21side_level_act21side_st04","storyGroup":"act21side","storySort":24,"storyDependence":"act21side_level_act21side_10_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"IS-ST-4","storyName":"缝合","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act21side/level_act21side_st04","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act21side_st04","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":22,"characters":["柳德米拉","？？？","红","激动的观众","兴奋的观众","莱昂图索","拉维妮娅","拉普兰德","扎罗"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/71/Avg_bg_33_g2_srcalley.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rainlight_loop","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shallowswalk","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","fadetime":"1","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":12},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"唔，尾巴弄湿了。","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"还真是一点都没变。无论是这些脏兮兮的街，还是烦死人的雨。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"不知道为什么，乌萨斯的雪能要人命，可还是这里的雨更让人不爽。","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"但愿老师家有吹风机......","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":18},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":19},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":20},{"type":"text","text":"老师家就在这条巷子的尽头。当年，弑君者怀着一腔怒火离开了这里，为了证明自己已经足够强大，能够向笼罩她的那片阴云复仇。","id":21},{"type":"text","text":"如今，柳德米拉又回来了。她的努力是否有给阴沉的天空打开一丝缺口，她自己都拿不准。","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"或许，其实什么都没改变，或许，她只是成了更大灾难的帮凶。","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"还好，柳德米拉还能回到这里，她想，老师一定能告诉她接下来应该怎么办。","id":24},{"type":"text","text":"突然，她感到一阵恶寒。","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"柳德米拉原本只是以为，这来源于自己即将再度面对老师的紧张。","id":26},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"但马上，她意识到自己错了。","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"她正在控制不住地战栗。","id":29},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":31},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shallowsrun","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":33},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":34},{"type":"dialog","id":35},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":36},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":37},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":38},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":39},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":40},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_bg_33_g8_srcroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":41},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":42},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":43},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$kjerag_n_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act14side/m_bat_kjerag_n_loop.mp3","volume":"0.5","id":44,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","id":45},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":46},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"老师！！","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":49},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_33_i16.png","xScale":"1.6","yScale":"1.6","y":"300","x":"350","fadetime":"1","id":50},{"type":"imagetween","duration":"10","xTo":"250","block":"false","id":51},{"type":"background","id":52},{"type":"character","id":53},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":54},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_33_i16.png","xScale":"1.7","yScale":"1.7","y":"300","x":"-100","fadetime":"1","id":55},{"type":"imagetween","duration":"10","xTo":"0","block":"false","id":56},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":57},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_33_i16.png","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","y":"150","fadetime":"1","id":58},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"0.88","yScaleTo":"0.88","duration":"30","yTo":"-20","block":"false","id":59},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":60},{"type":"text","text":"化不开的血腥味。","id":61},{"type":"text","text":"她的老师仰面倒在地上，鲜血仍在向外流淌蔓延。","id":62},{"type":"text","text":"一把小刀掉落一边。","id":63},{"type":"text","text":"柳德米拉想要靠近，压住老师仍在流血的伤口，但她发现自己无法挪动一步，她连视线都无法移开。","id":64},{"type":"text","text":"有一股让她熟悉，又让她恐惧的气息正从阴影中浮现。","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"穿着红色连帽衫，有着灰色头发的狼。","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"真狼死了，红听了外婆的话。","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"......是你。","id":68},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_bg_33_g8_srcroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":69},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"image","fadetime":"1.5","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":72},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","name2":"char_144_red_7#1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":73},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"0","block":"false","id":74},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":75},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","name2":"char_144_red_7#1","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"你......做了什么......","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","name2":"char_144_red_7#1","focus":"2","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"红是猎狼人，红听外婆的话。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_char_144_red_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"真狼死了，真狼没有反抗。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_char_144_red_1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":81},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","name2":"char_144_red_7#1","focus":"1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"你！！","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":84},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":85},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"300","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":86},{"type":"effect","name":"$e_slash_02_s","rox":"30","roy":"-200","roz":"-90","x":"100","y":"-60","layer":"1","id":87},{"type":"playsound","key":"$knifegore","id":88},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":89},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_ftrub","id":90},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"0.2","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":92},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"40","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"我杀了你！","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_144_red_7#1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"唔......红答应过凯尔希，只杀狼，你不是狼。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_char_144_red_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_144_red_7#3","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"原来如此，她是你的凯尔希吗？怪不得你身上有狼的气味。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_144_red_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.4","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"呼......呼......老师明明已经没办法再战斗了，你为什么还？！","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_144_red_7#1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"因为外婆告诉红，这就是游戏规则。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_char_144_red_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"现在，她出局啦。","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_char_144_red_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"红要走了，红还要找别的狼，他们就在附近。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_char_144_red_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_144_red_7#2","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"（嗅嗅）","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_char_144_red_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_144_red_7#7","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"红","text":"不过，好像还有一只狼也出局了，是有人比红的动作更快吗？","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_char_144_red_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.4","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"站住！","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"character","id":112},{"type":"text","text":"穿着红色连帽衫的狼没有回应柳德米拉的呼喊，她哼着破碎的小调，迈着轻快的步伐从柳德米拉身边掠过。","id":113},{"type":"text","text":"柳德米拉伸出的手停在了半空。","id":114},{"type":"text","text":"她突然想起，老师曾对她说：","id":115},{"type":"dialog","id":116},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":117},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“柳德米拉，你知道成为我的学生意味着什么吗？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":118},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我已经残废了，没什么大用，你却甘愿成为我的学生，我的工具？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":119},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我们都会后悔的，孩子。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":120},{"type":"subtitle","id":121},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"character","name":"char_1502_crowns","fadetime":"0.5","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.4","id":123},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":124},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-50","fadetime":"0.3","block":"false","id":125},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":126},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"柳德米拉跪倒在地。","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柳德米拉","text":"“吞下死难者的苦”......","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_char_1502_crowns.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":130},{"type":"dialog","id":131},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":132},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":134},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":135,"musicid":2},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_bg_33_g4_srctheater.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":136},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":138},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spotlightc","id":139},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":141},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_applause","id":142},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"不愧是卡特琳娜女士酝酿了如此之久的作品。","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"切利尼娜在剧中，作为一个完美的叙拉古人形象，到最后竟才被揭示出是一个所有叙拉古人构建出的幻象。","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"但是，正因为她在市井传闻中是众所周知的完美形象，用一种共同的想象去解释她竟也是合理的。","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"最后点出她并不存在的那一幕，实在是太让我震撼了。","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"真是意味深长的结尾。","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"前阵子的广播事件，还有后面那半天的混乱，我差点以为沃尔西尼就要这么完了。","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"结果现在还能看到这么优秀的作品，唉，活着还是有价值的啊。","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"可不是吗。","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"唉，我当时以为天都要塌下来了。","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"没想到最后会是那样的结果。","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"哎，你打不打算搬去新城市？","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"看情况吧，不过，如果新城市也有卡特琳娜女士的作品，我应该会去吧。","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"毕竟......家族不会入驻的城市，我长这么大都没敢想过。","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"这么说起来......你知道吗？","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"卡特琳娜女士好像在筹备一部新的作品。","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的观众","text":"新的作品？","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"对，这部作品光是标题，就已经足够吸引人了。","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"兴奋的观众","text":"叫做——《叙拉古人》。","id":161},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":162},{"type":"dialog","id":163},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":164},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":166},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":167,"musicid":3},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rainheavy_loop","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":168},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_bg_33_g5_srcpark.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":171},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shovel","volume":"0.7","id":172},{"type":"text","text":"一铲，又一铲。","id":173},{"type":"text","text":"墓园之中，莱昂图索正在奋力地挖掘着墓穴。","id":174},{"type":"text","text":"他的身边是一口棺木，里面躺着他的父亲——贝纳尔多。","id":175},{"type":"text","text":"今天是曾经的贝洛内家族领袖，贝纳尔多的葬礼。","id":176},{"type":"text","text":"身为十二家族之一的领袖，参加其葬礼的人原本应当挤满整个墓园。","id":177},{"type":"text","text":"然而，没有人会参加一个背叛了家族，背叛了城市，背叛了时代之人的葬礼。","id":178},{"type":"text","text":"莱昂图索也谢绝了拉维妮娅等人的参加。","id":179},{"type":"text","text":"这是他与父亲最后的告别。","id":180},{"type":"dialog","id":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"父亲，你说，后人会怎么评价你呢。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"是开创了新时代的人，还是背叛了旧时代的人？","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#3$1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"或许，这要看我接下来的成果而定吧，哈哈。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#2$1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"你真是给我出了个大难题啊。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#8$1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"不过，该说我不愧是你的儿子吗，也是真亏我接住了。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":193},{"type":"character","id":194},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shovel","volume":"0.7","id":195},{"type":"text","text":"莱昂图索一边挖着，一边像是父亲还活着一样，轻快地说着。","id":196},{"type":"text","text":"除此之外，他不知道还能说些什么。","id":197},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"对了，西西里夫人同意了我的请求。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"新的移动城市，将不会有家族入驻。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"你的梦想也算是实现了一部分吧。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"在和西西里夫人交流过后，我终于理解了一点。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"这一位丝毫不介意在死后将叙拉古带入墓穴。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"她对于叙拉古只能在她活着时维持和平毫无负担，叙拉古不需要未来。","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"该怎么说呢......西西里夫人，比起一个统治者，她似乎更像是一个旧时代的看守者。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"她愿意给我机会，也只是因为，我给出的答案，让她认为或许可以尝试一下，仅此而已。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"真是一位可怕的存在。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......哦，原本以为要挖个半天，没想到，比我想得要轻松一些。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":220},{"type":"character","id":221},{"type":"text","text":"墓穴的大小已经足够，剩下的，就是将棺木埋入其中。","id":222},{"type":"text","text":"莱昂图索走到棺木前，犹豫了一下，但终于还是伸出手。","id":223},{"type":"text","text":"棺木很沉，他推起来很费力。","id":224},{"type":"text","text":"而就在他感到吃力时，他感觉到，身边忽然出现了一个人在帮他推。","id":225},{"type":"text","text":"他转头看去，那是德米特里。","id":226},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dragsofa","loop":"true","channel":"b","id":228},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":229},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"b","fadetime":"1","id":230},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":231},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"15","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":232},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown3","id":233},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":234},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"德米特里，你......","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":237},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_33_i07.png","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","x":"-200","fadetime":"1","id":238},{"type":"imagetween","duration":"60","xTo":"-150","block":"false","id":239},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":240},{"type":"character","id":241},{"type":"text","text":"德米特里没有说话，他只是从自己外套的口袋里，掏出一样微微闪着银光的东西，丢入墓穴中。","id":242},{"type":"text","text":"那是一块怀表。","id":243},{"type":"dialog","id":244},{"type":"subtitle","text":"这是首领......这是他曾经送我的怀表。","x":"500","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":245},{"type":"subtitle","id":246},{"type":"subtitle","text":"现在，也算是物归原主了。","x":"400","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":247},{"type":"subtitle","id":248},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"250","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":249},{"type":"subtitle","id":250},{"type":"subtitle","text":"你已经向我道过歉了，莱昂图索。","x":"500","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":251},{"type":"subtitle","id":252},{"type":"subtitle","text":"只不过，即使我可以原谅你，在这次动乱里死去的兄弟也不会原谅你。","x":"700","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"400","id":253},{"type":"subtitle","id":254},{"type":"subtitle","text":"即使贝洛内家族不复存在，我也不会忘记他们。","x":"500","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":255},{"type":"subtitle","id":256},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我听说了，你打算重组一个新的家族。","x":"250","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":257},{"type":"subtitle","id":258},{"type":"subtitle","text":"活下来的大部分人都离开了，但是，依然有留下来的人，他们需要一个安身之所。","x":"700","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"450","id":259},{"type":"subtitle","id":260},{"type":"subtitle","text":"即使那在你看来，是落后的家族。","x":"450","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":261},{"type":"subtitle","id":262},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......这样也好。","x":"250","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":263},{"type":"subtitle","id":264},{"type":"subtitle","text":"你走的是一条荆棘之路。","x":"400","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":265},{"type":"subtitle","id":266},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我知道。","x":"250","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":267},{"type":"subtitle","id":268},{"type":"subtitle","text":"到时候，我依然会拦在你的路上。","x":"450","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":269},{"type":"subtitle","id":270},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我知道。","x":"250","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":271},{"type":"subtitle","id":272},{"type":"subtitle","text":"别随便死了。","x":"300","y":"250","alignment":"right","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":273},{"type":"subtitle","id":274},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"imagetween","duration":"5","xTo":"0","block":"false","id":276},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":277},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shallowswalk","id":278},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_33_i07.png","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","x":"150","fadetime":"1.5","id":279},{"type":"imagetween","duration":"30","xTo":"200","block":"false","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":281},{"type":"text","text":"雨点的声音嘈杂，但莱昂图索依然听到了最后这句话的末尾，有一声轻轻的“莱昂”。","id":282},{"type":"dialog","id":283},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":284},{"type":"image","fadetime":"1.5","id":285},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":286},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":287},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"你也是，德米特。","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":290},{"type":"text","text":"他抬起头，任由雨点打在脸上。","id":291},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"3","id":293},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":294},{"type":"dialog","id":295},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":298},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_bg_33_g11_mansionhall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":299},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":301},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","fadetime":"1","id":302},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":303},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"这些家具，大部分都用不上了吧。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"毕竟，贝洛内家族已经不复存在了。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"绝大多数曾经的家族成员已经离开了这里，他们......任何人都很难接受来自自己领袖的背叛。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"贝纳尔多这个几乎已经站在家族统治最高点的人，却否定了家族的存在本身。","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"也否定了很多我们曾视若珍宝的东西。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"荣耀、信任、忠诚、为了家族的奉献......","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"父亲曾教导每一位家族成员遵守这些规矩，到头来，他自己却从未相信过这些吗？","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......我不知道。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"这几天，我时常在想。我有曾触及过那个真正的贝纳尔多·贝洛内吗？","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"白日剧团的艺术总监是他的伪装，贝洛内家族老谋深算的领袖是他的伪装......","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"那么有没有可能，那个曾和我谈起他的理想，带着笑容，两眼放光的贝纳尔多也是他的伪装呢？","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"不重要了，已经不那么重要了。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"莱昂，你和他，一起让那座新的城市真正有了诞生的机会。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"或许吧。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"搬家的车很快就会来了。","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......我知道了。","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"这一切并不是徒劳无功，莱昂。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"我知道。","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"我们会在新城区......不，现在是新城市了，建起些新的东西的。","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"叙拉古未曾出现过的，崭新的——","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"属于每个人的秩序。","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"莱昂图索看向拉维妮娅，他的眼中，闪烁着果决。","id":340},{"type":"dialog","id":341},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"subtitle","text":"文明。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.5","width":"700","id":343},{"type":"subtitle","id":344},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":345},{"type":"dialog","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":348},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":349},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":350,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":351},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":352},{"type":"text","text":"自诞生那一刻起，每一头狼都知道，自己的存在即是荒野的象征。","id":353},{"type":"text","text":"经过漫长的时光，无数次的厮杀，他们最终选择了以如今这种游戏的方式选出头狼。","id":354},{"type":"text","text":"对扎罗来说，这一局的惨败无疑是他的耻辱。","id":355},{"type":"text","text":"但他们生生不息。","id":356},{"type":"text","text":"只要等到下一轮游戏开始，他马上就能卷土重来。","id":357},{"type":"text","text":"为此，他已经开始了物色人选。","id":358},{"type":"text","text":"并且，他立刻发现了离开沃尔西尼，漫步于荒野的拉普兰德。","id":359},{"type":"text","text":"然而——","id":360},{"type":"dialog","id":361},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#6$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":362},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"哈......哈......","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#10$1","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"休息够了吗，扎罗。","id":366,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":367},{"type":"character","id":368},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_688_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":370},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_688_1#1$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扎罗","text":"......","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_688_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":373},{"type":"text","text":"扎罗与拉普兰德在荒野上战斗了三个月。","id":374},{"type":"text","text":"期间，扎罗有无数次机会咬开这个狂人的脖子。","id":375},{"type":"text","text":"她绝无可能真的战胜他。","id":376},{"type":"text","text":"但是，他却逐渐明白，是他，绝无可能战胜她。","id":377},{"type":"text","text":"她的血肉无法滋养任何思想，她的头颅无法称颂任何胜利，她的死亡毫无意义。","id":378},{"type":"text","text":"她是一具被填满的空壳。","id":379},{"type":"text","text":"她也是荒野？","id":380},{"type":"text","text":"不，她是荒芜。","id":381},{"type":"text","text":"他在一瞬间理解，如果贝纳尔多的背叛是一种意料之外的情理之中，那么眼前的存在，在他的理解之外。","id":382},{"type":"text","text":"不，他也曾见过这样的人类，她绝非独一无二。","id":383},{"type":"text","text":"但她却是其中唯一一个在这独一无二的时刻出现在他面前的人。","id":384},{"type":"text","text":"一种预兆。","id":385},{"type":"text","text":"一种呼唤。","id":386},{"type":"text","text":"于是，千百年来，荒野的化身，第一次，或许也将是最后一次向一个人类伏下身躯。","id":387},{"type":"text","text":"他选择向未知放下尊严。","id":388},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#1$1","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"不打了？","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b7/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_688_1#1$1","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扎罗","text":"我们的斗争将会持续千年万年。","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_688_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_688_1#1$1","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扎罗","text":"在分出胜负之前，我会与你同行。","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_688_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#8$1","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"哈，随你的便。","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":397},{"type":"text","text":"拉普兰德无力地丢下武器，她的身体早已失去知觉。","id":398},{"type":"text","text":"在她倒下之前，扎罗走过去，理所当然一般地，用自己的身躯托住了她。","id":399},{"type":"dialog","id":400},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"20","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":401},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","volume":"0.6","id":402},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"德克萨斯，我们选择了不同的道路毁灭叙拉古。","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"我很期待，我们下一次的见面。","id":405},{"type":"dialog","id":406},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_dim_closeeye","layer":"1","id":407},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":408},{"type":"dialog","id":409},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":410},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":411},{"type":"text","text":"她闭上双眼，沉沉睡去。","id":412},{"type":"text","text":"苍茫的原野上别无他物，一时间，仿佛天地之间，只剩下一人，一狼。","id":413},{"type":"dialog","id":414},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":415},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_wolflordroar_1","volume":"0.7","id":416},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":417},{"type":"subtitle","text":"蛮荒。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.5","width":"700","id":418},{"type":"subtitle","id":419},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":420},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"image","id":422},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":423},{"type":"character","id":424},{"type":"image","id":425}],"characters":["柳德米拉","？？？","红","激动的观众","兴奋的观众","莱昂图索","拉维妮娅","拉普兰德","扎罗"]}